notes_display: A picture book inspired by a brief strike by Hong Kong hospital workers calling for the border with mainland China to be completely sealed at the beginning of the coronavirus pandemic in February 2020. Page 2 lists the impact of the COVID-19 upon Hong Kong, based on statistics collected until March 8, 2021.
